{"id":906,"parent_id":905,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":906,"title":"Joel 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Joel","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","Joel"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Call a solemn assembly and gather to the house of the Lord, for the day of the Lord is at hand."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.1","order":"02.30.001.60765"},["b","1"],"The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that came to Joel the son of Pethuel."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.2","order":"02.30.001.60766"},["b","2"],"Hear this, ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"old men"],", and give ear, all ye",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"inhabitants"],"of the land. Hath this been in your days, or even in the days of your fathers?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.3","order":"02.30.001.60767"},["b","3"],"Tell ye your children of it, and",["i","let"],"your children",["i","tell"],"their children, and their children another generation."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.4","order":"02.30.001.60768"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"That"],"which the palmerworm hath left hath the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"locust"],"eaten; and that which the locust hath left hath the cankerworm eaten; and that which the cankerworm hath left hath the caterpiller eaten."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.5","order":"02.30.001.60769"},["b","5"],"Awake, ye drunkards, and weep; and howl, all ye drinkers of wine, because of the new wine; for it is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"cut off"],"from your mouth."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.6","order":"02.30.001.60770"},["b","6"],"For a nation is come up upon my land, strong, and without",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"number"],", whose",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"teeth"],["i","are"],"the teeth of a lion, and he hath the cheek teeth of a great lion."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.7","order":"02.30.001.60771"},["b","7"],"He hath laid my vine waste, and barked my fig tree: he hath made it clean bare, and cast",["i","it"],"away; the branches thereof are made white."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.8","order":"02.30.001.60772"},["b","8"],"¶Lament like a virgin girded with sackcloth for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"husband"],"of her youth."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.9","order":"02.30.001.60773"},["b","9"],"The meat offering and the drink offering is cut off from the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; the priests, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s ministers, mourn."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.10","order":"02.30.001.60774"},["b","10"],"The field is wasted, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"land"],"mourneth; for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"corn"],"is wasted: the new wine is dried up, the oil languisheth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.11","order":"02.30.001.60775"},["b","11"],"Be ye ashamed, O ye husbandmen; howl, O ye vinedressers, for the wheat and for the barley; because the harvest of the field is perished."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.12","order":"02.30.001.60776"},["b","12"],"The vine is dried up, and the fig tree languisheth; the pomegranate tree, the palm tree also, and the apple tree,",["i","even"],"all the trees of the field, are withered: because",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"joy"],"is withered away from the sons of men."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.13","order":"02.30.001.60777"},["b","13"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Gird"],"yourselves, and lament, ye priests: howl, ye ministers of the altar: come, lie all night in sackcloth, ye ministers of my God: for the meat offering and the drink offering is withholden from the house of your God."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.14","order":"02.30.001.60778"},["b","14"],"¶Sanctify ye a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"fast"],", call a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"solemn assembly"],", gather the elders",["i","and"],"all the inhabitants of the land",["i","into"],"the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, and cry unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],","],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.15","order":"02.30.001.60779"},["b","15"],"Alas for the day! for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"at hand, and as a destruction from the Almighty shall it come."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.16","order":"02.30.001.60780"},["b","16"],"Is not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"meat"],"cut off before our eyes,",["i","yea,"],"joy and gladness from the house of our God?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.17","order":"02.30.001.60781"},["b","17"],"The seed is rotten under their clods, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"garners"],"are laid desolate, the barns are broken down; for the corn is withered."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.18","order":"02.30.001.60782"},["b","18"],"How do the beasts groan! the herds of cattle are perplexed, because they have no pasture; yea, the flocks of sheep are made desolate."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.19","order":"02.30.001.60783"},["b","19"],"O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", to thee will I cry: for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"fire"],"hath devoured the pastures of the wilderness, and the flame hath burned all the trees of the field."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.20","order":"02.30.001.60784"},["b","20"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"beasts"],"of the field cry also unto thee: for the rivers of waters are dried up, and the fire hath devoured the pastures of the wilderness."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.2a","order":"02.30.001.60785"},["b","2a"],["span.small","HEB"],"elders."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.2b","order":"02.30.001.60787"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.6"},"D&C 1:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.4a","order":"02.30.001.60789"},["b","4a"],["span.small","IE"],"The invading or conquering armies are compared to four varieties (or stages of growth) of locusts."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.4b","order":"02.30.001.60791"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.24.14-38"},"Lev. 26:24 (14–38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.5a","order":"02.30.001.60793"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/32.10"},"Isa. 32:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.6a","order":"02.30.001.60795"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/9.16"},"Rev. 9:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.6b","order":"02.30.001.60797"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/9.8"},"Rev. 9:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.8a","order":"02.30.001.60799"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.32.32-38"},"Ezek. 16:32 (32–38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.10a","order":"02.30.001.60801"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.3"},"Hosea 4:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.25.24-25"},"D&C 43:25 (24–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/87.6.1-8"},"87:6 (1–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-m/1.29"},"JS—M 1:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.10b","order":"02.30.001.60803"},["b","10b"],["span.small","OR"],"grain."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.12a","order":"02.30.001.60805"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.11"},"Isa. 24:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.13a","order":"02.30.001.60807"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.8"},"Jer. 4:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.14a","order":"02.30.001.60809"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fast-fasting"},"TG Fast, Fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.14b","order":"02.30.001.60811"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/solemn-assembly"},"TG Solemn Assembly"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.15a","order":"02.30.001.60813"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.10"},"Jer. 46:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.18"},"Amos 5:18"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/day-of-the-lord"},"TG Day of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.16a","order":"02.30.001.60815"},["b","16a"],["span.small","OR"],"food."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.17a","order":"02.30.001.60817"},["b","17a"],["span.small","OR"],"storehouses."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.19a","order":"02.30.001.60819"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.18"},"Zeph. 1:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.15.14-15"},"2 Ne. 6:15 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.77"},"Jacob 5:77"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.3"},"6:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.21"},"D&C 29:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.41.40-41"},"45:41 (40–41)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.26.25-26"},"97:26 (25–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.20a","order":"02.30.001.60821"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.22.21-22"},"Joel 2:22 (21–22)"],"."]]}
